---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | My Blog"
  description="Learn more about this blog and its mission to share web development knowledge."
>
  <div class="container content" style="padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 3rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center;">About This Blog</h1>
    
    <div class="article__content">
      <p>
        Welcome to my blog! This is a space where I share my thoughts, learnings, and experiences
        in web development, programming, and technology.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <p>
        This blog covers a wide range of topics including:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Modern JavaScript and TypeScript</li>
        <li>Web frameworks like Astro, React, and more</li>
        <li>CSS and modern web design</li>
        <li>Best practices and coding patterns</li>
        <li>Performance optimization</li>
        <li>SEO and accessibility</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Built With Modern Tech</h2>
      <p>
        This blog is built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>,
        a modern static site generator that prioritizes performance and developer experience.
      </p>
      
      <p>Key features include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Lightning-fast page loads with static site generation</li>
        <li>SEO optimized with proper meta tags and structured data</li>
        <li>Full-text search powered by Pagefind</li>
        <li>RSS feed for easy subscription</li>
        <li>Dark mode and reading mode for comfortable reading</li>
        <li>Mobile-responsive design</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        I love connecting with fellow developers and readers. Feel free to reach out via:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Twitter: <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@yourusername</a></li>
        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@yourusername</a></li>
        <li>Email: your.email@example.com</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>
        Subscribe to the <a href="/rss.xml">RSS feed</a> to stay updated with new posts!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
